  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO CREATE THE ONE FAIR WAGE ACT; TO PROVIDE DEFINITIONS; TO ESTABLISH A STATE MINIMUM WAGE; TO PROVIDE FOR INCREASES IN THE MINIMUM WAGE; TO PROVIDE THE MINIMUM WAGE FOR TIPPED EMPLOYEES; TO PROVIDE THAT THIS LAW SHALL NOT CONFLICT WITH ANY FEDERAL LAW; TO PROVIDE A SEVERABILITY CLAUSE; TO PROVIDE THAT THIS ACT SHALL BE PROSPECTIVE ONLY; TO BRING FORWARD SECTIONS 7-7-204, 17-1-51, 23-15-239, 25-3-40, 37-7-307, 57-34-5, 85-3-4, 97-3-54.4 AND 99-19-20, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, FOR PURPOSES OF POSSIBLE AMENDMENT; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
  },
